FOLDER KdV

* NOTEBOOKS
	- kdv_fvfourier.ipynb -> kdv.py
		:: Finite volume solvers for the advection step
		:: Fourier (periodic case) and Finite Difference (non periodic case) schemes for the dispersive step
		:: Splitting scheme (main) : runRk4FVFourier(..,periodic=,...)
		:: Validation with some examples using the criteria based on the scale analysis
	- kdv_BC
		:: Motivational examples
		:: Optimization of Robin conditions (up to 1st and 2nd derivatives) as TBCs

* PYTHON SCRIPTS :
	- kdv.py





